race_simplicity 16 Player Rally Race Map
Difficulty Level: Easy
2 Laps to win
Jump on the straightaway between turns 2 and 3
Race high in the sky on a relatively simple map. :)
This map is for Rally Race servers only!! Rally Race is a SourceMod plugin, you must have Rally Race installed or else this map will be pointless because there are no CT spawns.
